highlights.text: “The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Australia the longest, at 102 days straight.
“If It Makes You Happy - triple j Like A Version” by Skegss is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Australia, up 12 spots at #88.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Australia. “Golden” is the highest at #6.
“Predador de Perereca” by BLOW RECORDS and Mc Jhey is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Australia at #1.
